Package: alphainfo
Type: Package
Title: R Client for the alphainfo.io Structural Intelligence API
Version: 1.5.16
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "QGI Quantum Systems",
      family = "LTDA",
      email = "contato@alphainfo.io",
      role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
      comment = c(ORCID = NA_character_)
    )
  )
Description: Detect structural regime changes in any time series — biomedical
    signals, financial markets, energy grids, seismic data, IoT sensors,
    network traffic. Thin tidy client for the alphainfo.io Structural
    Intelligence API. Honest fingerprint contract (returns NA when the
    engine cannot decompose a signal, never silent zeros) and public
    constants kept in sync with the server. Requires a free API key from
    <https://alphainfo.io/register>.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://alphainfo.io, https://github.com/qgidev/alphainfo-r
BugReports: https://github.com/qgidev/alphainfo-r/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
